title: WIN AND YOU'RE IN (PLAYOFFS)
description:
The crew breaks down what's to come in week 18. They'll discuss the playoff implications that are on the line. Bruce Arians spoke about the AB situation, plus we have updates on Derrick Henry's return for the Titans.
